why: Bumped into someone walking out of 370 Jay St. building

Documenting the previous 'sorry' in my phone while walking to a donor kebab place with my team mate. Realized it's rude to look at your phone while someone else is talking. I had to explain what and why I was writing.
Doner Kebab staff was voicing that he is sad no one listens to him, so I said “sorry no one listens to you”
